        p Hi, I’m Oliver &mdash; programmer; serial founder; amateur juggler; husband; father of two.

        p.
          I've worked at
          <a href="http://apple.com">Apple</a> (consumer electronics and computers),
          <a href="https://nest.com">Nest</a> (wifi-connected learning thermostats),
          AOL Palo Alto (during the reboot &mdash; not as stodgy as it sounds),
          and a bunch of start-ups.

        p.
          Based in Amherst, Massachusetts &mdash; I’ve spent most of my life commuting to Boston
          and/or telecommuting to California.

        p.
