      section#code
        h2 Code
        p I consider coding (like writing) as a way to think clearly, and as a means of self-expression.
        p Good code is beautiful. (Not all code needs to be good.)
        p.
          I currently work mostly in Ruby, Python, and JavaScript / CoffeeScript;
          previously in C, C++, Common Lisp, Java, SmallTalk, assembly, and Dylan;
          and some smaller projects in Haskell, Objective C, and <tt>bash</tt>.
          For server work I've used mostly Rails, Django, Sinatra, and Express; MySQL, Postgres, and Redis;
          Apache and nginx; and <abbr>AWS</abbr> (and previously DreamHost, SliceHost, and colos).

